TOTAL ENERGY DIAGNOSTICS
========================

To compute total energy diagnostics

1. go to your run directory
2. (optional) Usually the history files are averaged:

	source ~/git-scripts/ncl_scripts/ave.sh case h2

3. assuming that your history file is case.h2.ave.nc execute

        source ~/git-scripts/ncl_scripts/budgets/te_budgets.sh case.h2.ave.nc

  Please note that this script needs atm_in and drv_in files from the run directory so
  that the different time-steps used in the dynamical core can be computed


NAMELIST
========

fincl for a dry drynamical core run is (note: double precision output is required):

 fincl2 = 'SE_dED', 'KE_dED', 'SE_dAF', 'KE_dAF', 'SE_dBD', 'KE_dBD', 'SE_dAD', 'KE_dAD', 'SE_dAR', 'KE_dAR', 'SE_dBF',
          'KE_dBF', 'SE_dBH', 'KE_dBH', 'SE_dCH', 'KE_dCH', 'SE_dAH', 'KE_dAH'
 nhtfrq = 0
 ndens  = 1


fincl for a moist simulation (note: double precision is required):

 fincl2 = 'WV_pBF','WL_pBF','WI_pBF','SE_pBF','KE_pBF',
          'WV_pBP','WL_pBP','WI_pBP','SE_pBP','KE_pBP',
          'WV_pAP','WL_pAP','WI_pAP','SE_pAP','KE_pAP',
          'WV_pAM','WL_pAM','WI_pAM','SE_pAM','KE_pAM',
          'WV_dED','WL_dED','WI_dED','SE_dED','KE_dED',
          'WV_dAF','WL_dAF','WI_dAF','SE_dAF','KE_dAF',
          'WV_dBD','WL_dBD','WI_dBD','SE_dBD','KE_dBD',
          'WV_dAD','WL_dAD','WI_dAD','SE_dAD','KE_dAD',
          'WV_dAR','WL_dAR','WI_dAR','SE_dAR','KE_dAR',
          'WV_dBF','WL_dBF','WI_dBF','SE_dBF','KE_dBF',
          'WV_dBH','WL_dBH','WI_dBH','SE_dBH','KE_dBH',
          'WV_dCH','WL_dCH','WI_dCH','SE_dCH','KE_dCH',
          'WV_dAH','WL_dAH','WI_dAH','SE_dAH','KE_dAH' 

